/'
Defines Relations
'/

' used to merge inheritance arrows header.
skinparam groupInheritance 2
Person <|--  Student
Person <|--  Parent

Student "1..*" - "0..*" Parent

Student "1..*" - "1..*" Classroom
(Student, Classroom) .. StudentClass

Parent "0..*" - "0..*" Classroom
(Parent, Classroom) .. ParentClass

Student "0..*" - "0..*" Course
(Student, Course) .. Score
@enduml